msgstr "贊助者與支持者"

#: ../../../sponsors.rst:4
msgid ""
"Please consider sponsoring urllib3 development, especially if your company "
"benefits from this library."
msgstr "請考慮贊助 urllib3 的開發，特別是如果您的公司受益於此程式庫。"

#: ../../../sponsors.rst:7
