msgstr ""

#: ../../../sponsors.rst:52
msgid ""
"A grant for contiguous full-time development has the biggest impact for "
"progress. Periods of 3 to 10 days allow a contributor to tackle substantial "
"complex issues which are otherwise left to linger until somebody can't "
"afford to not fix them."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../sponsors.rst:57
msgid ""
"Contact `@sethmlarson <https://github.com/sethmlarson>`_ or `@shazow "
"<https://github.com/shazow>`_ to arrange a grant for a core contributor."
msgstr ""
"請聯絡 `@sethmlarson <https://github.com/sethmlarson>`_ 或 `@shazow <https://"
"github.com/shazow>`_ 為核心貢獻者安排一筆資助。"

#: ../../../sponsors.rst:60
msgid ""
"We also welcome sponsorship in the form of time. We greatly appreciate "
"companies who encourage employees to contribute on an ongoing basis during "
"their work hours. Let us know and we'll be glad to add you to our sponsors "
"list."
msgstr ""
"我們也歡迎以時間投入的方式進行贊助。我們非常感謝那些鼓勵員工在工作時間內持續"
"貢獻力量的公司。請與我們聯繫，我們將很樂意將您增添到我們的贊助者名單中。"

